<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.5.3">
<l>ulavu tiraiyuṅ kulavaraiyu mūḻi mutalā veṇtikkum</l>
<l>nilavuñ cuṭaru miruḷumāy niṉṟāṉ veṉṟi viṟalāḻi</l>
<l>valavaṉ vāṉōrt tamperumāṉ</l>
<l>maruvā varakkark keññāṉṟum</l>
<l>calavaṉ calamcūḻn taḻakāya cāḷak kirāma maṭaineñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Heart, take refuge at Śālagrāma which is beautiful with water [all] around,</l>
<l>[The place of ] him who endures as crashing waves and mountain ranges,</l>
<l rend="indent">the eight directions including the eons,</l>
<l>The moon, the sun, and darkness, who is always the enemy</l>
<l rend="indent">of the hostile demons,</l>
<l>The one skilled with the strong, victory discus, great lord of the celestials.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
